    dc:description "Figure 3. Morphological details of some Cryptotropidae. A, stylet protruding from the genital atrium of Renschetrema sp. B, C, eggs released from the uterus of Pseudocryptotropa surniculi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8426195/files/figure.png" ;
